OL,4,CLiverpool City Council gave contract to
OL,5,Cmayor's son's company
OL,6, Liverpool City Council awarded a
OL,7, contract to a firm run by a son of
OL,8, then-mayor Joe Anderson, despite it not
OL,9, being on an approved contractors' list.
OL,11,FA government-commissioned report has
OL,12,Frevealed Site Safety Consultants (SSC)
OL,13,Fgot the deal managing health and safety
OL,14,Fwork when a flyover was demolished.
OL,16,FSSC chief executive David Anderson said
OL,17,Fhe was considering defamation action in
OL,18,Frelation to the report's claims.
OL,20,FThe government is appointing officials
OL,21,Fto oversee parts of the council.
